    <div class="hdr-eyebrow">Public Accountability Initiative &middot; Dallas, Texas</div>
    <h1 class="hdr-title">White Rock Boathouse: The Public Deserves Better</h1>
    <p class="hdr-sub">Documenting three documented failures at a city-owned public facility — and the City of Dallas's refusal to address them.</p>
